com.credenceid.biometrics

Interface Biometrics.MRZStatusListener

  • Enclosing interface:
    Biometrics

    public static interface Biometrics.MRZStatusListener
    Interface definition for callbacks to be invoked when a request to either Biometrics.openMRZ(MRZStatusListener listener) or Biometrics.closeMRZ() returns with a result. These methods may also be invoked whenever MRZ sensor opens/closes.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onMRZClose(Biometrics.ResultCode resultCode, Biometrics.CloseReasonCode reasonCode)
      Invoked when a request to Biometrics.closeMRZ() ()} returns with result or MZ reader closes for any Biometrics.CloseReasonCode.
      void onMRZOpen(Biometrics.ResultCode resultCode)
      Invoked when a request to Biometrics.openMRZ(MRZStatusListener) returns with a result.

    • Method Detail

      • onMRZOpen

        void onMRZOpen(Biometrics.ResultCode resultCode)
        Invoked when a request to Biometrics.openMRZ(MRZStatusListener) returns with a result. Is also invoked whenever MRZ sensor opens.
        Parameters:
        resultCode - Biometrics.ResultCode.OK if sensor successfully opened, Biometrics.ResultCode.FAIL} if sensor failed to open. Biometrics.ResultCode.INTERMEDIATE} is returned while sensor is in middle of operation.

      • onMRZClose

        void onMRZClose(Biometrics.ResultCode resultCode,
                Biometrics.CloseReasonCode reasonCode)
        Invoked when a request to Biometrics.closeMRZ() ()} returns with result or MZ reader closes for any Biometrics.CloseReasonCode.
        Parameters:
        resultCode - Biometrics.ResultCode.OK if fingerprint reader was successfully closed. Biometrics.ResultCode.FAIL} if fingerprint reader failed to close. Biometrics.ResultCode.INTERMEDIATE} this code is never returned for this API.
        reasonCode - See Biometrics.CloseReasonCode.
